OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice investigate hate crime
OL,4,Cincidents targeting Jehovah's Witnesses
OL,6,FPolice have released a CCTV image of a
OL,7,Fman they'd like to speak to following
OL,8,Fa reported hate crime in Somerset.
OL,10,FAvon and Somerset Police said a letter
OL,11,Fconsidered threatening was left at an
OL,12,Faddress of Jehovah's Witnesses at
OL,13,Faround 8:20pm on Friday 20 March in
OL,14,FMinehead.
OL,16,FOfficers have carried out CCTV, house-
OL,17,Fto-house, and forensic enquiries, and
OL,18,Fhave since released a picture of a man
OL,19,Fthey'd like to speak to.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
