FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice investigate hate crime
OL,4,Cincidents targeting Jehovah's Witnesses
OL,6,FThe man pictured is described as
OL,7,Fwearing a white cowboy-style hat, with
OL,8,Fchequered trousers, and a jumper with
OL,9,Fa white stripe down the sleeve.
OL,11,FPolice say the man may have been seen
OL,12,Fin town centre areas that evening too,
OL,13,Fand would like to speak to anyone who
OL,14,Fmay have seen him.
OL,16,FA man, in his fifties, has been
OL,17,Farrested in connection with the
OL,18,Fincident and has been released on
OL,19,Fconditional bail while the
OL,20,Finvestigation continues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
