FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice investigate hate crime
OL,4,Cincidents targeting Jehovah's Witnesses
OL,6,FThe letter is the latest incident in a
OL,7,Fseries of hate crimes targeting the
OL,8,FChristian group and the Kingdom Hall
OL,9,Fin Mart Road.
OL,11,FDC Louis Morris, from Avon and
OL,12,FSomerset Police, said: "This is the
OL,13,Flatest in a series of incidents
OL,14,Frelating to a wider investigation into
OL,15,Fhate crime targeting the Jehovah's
OL,16,FWitness community, and we continue to
OL,17,Fwork closely with community groups and
OL,18,Ffaith organisations to offer support
OL,19,Fand to make sure everyone feels safe.
OL,26,@tD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1776265866
OL,3,CPolice investigate hate crime
OL,4,Cincidents targeting Jehovah's Witnesses
OL,6,F"We would urge anybody who may have
OL,7,Fany relevant information which could
OL,8,Fassist with our investigation, no
OL,9,Fmatter how small or trivial they may
OL,10,Ffeel it is, and those with concerns
OL,11,Fare urged to speak to our
OL,12,Fneighbourhood officers who are visible
OL,13,Fconducting reassurance patrols.
OL,15,F"There is absolutely no place in our
OL,16,Fcommunities for hate crime, and we
OL,17,Fwould urge anybody who witnesses such
OL,18,Fincidents to report them because we
OL,19,Fwill investigate them fully and ensure
OL,20,Fjustice is served."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@SO]
